ObjectProperty: <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00143>

    Annotations: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "\"This statue consists of (a portion of) gold and (a portion of) silver.\" 

In this example (a portion of) gold and (a portion of) silver are both object aggregates that consists of gold and silver atoms, respectively."@en,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "x consists of y iff 
- x is a material entity
- y is an object aggregate 
- x is on a higher level of granularity than y 
- all components of y are part of x 
- all parts of x overlap with some parts of y."@en,
        rdfs:label "consists of"@en
    
    
ObjectProperty: <https://w3id.org/coato/coat_00003>

    Annotations: 
        rdfs:label "has start time"@en,
        rdfs:seeAlso "The start time of a process is the first instant of the temporal region the process occupies. The start time of a process bounary is identical with the temporal instant the process boundary occupies."@en,
        rdfs:seeAlso "http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_000680"
    
    SubPropertyOf: 
        owl:topObjectProperty
    
    SubPropertyChain: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000199> o <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000222>
    
