    Annotations: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A pump is a device that is designed to move and regulate the flow of a fluid, such as a liquid or gas, by generating a pressure difference that causes the fluid to be transported from one location to another.",
        rdfs:label "Pumpe"@de,
        rdfs:label "pump"@en
    
    SubClassOf: 
