Class: <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00117>

    Annotations: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A mixture is a chemical substance composed of multiple molecules, at least two of which are of a different kind."@en,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "The axiom should really say: 
'has part' min 2 'mixture component'
However, according to Hermit part_of is not a simple property (probably because it is used as part of a role composition), and, thus, the restrictions of OWL prevent its use in cardinality restrictions.",
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "ChEBI"@en,
        rdfs:label "mixture"@en,
        rdfs:seeAlso "CHEBI:60004"@en
    
    SubClassOf: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_59999>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> some <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00148>
    
    
