        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> some <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00131>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> exactly 1 <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00148>
    
    
