Class: <https://w3id.org/coato/#coat_00158>

    Annotations: 
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "The plasma emission intensity is the amount of electromagnetic radiation (light) emitted by atoms or ions in a plasma when they are excited by energy."@en,
        rdfs:label "plasma emission intensity"@en
    
